## Quick agent commands

```powershell
cd "C:\Users\Mr. Dev Mishra\Documents\Projects\cloudflare-security-lab"
gh auth status
git push origin main
```

If `gh auth status` fails, use `GH_TOKEN` bootstrap from `git credential fill` (see global rule Step 3). Do **not** run `gh auth login` headlessly — it needs a browser for `read:org` scope.
